When ever a customer enters the restaurant the manager issues him the menu card and the customer has to choose the items from menu list as follows:
Select any of the main menu options displayed on the screen by entering the titles displayed
Once we select one of the menu option then we get sub items in that main menu element with corrresponding id's
Select the no.of sub items by entering the id's of the elements displyed
If you are done with ordering enter '-1' to exit from menu
Once you complete the order the manager orders the master chef wgo inturn orders his cochefs during which the customer will be waiting for the order
Once the order is done server brings the order and serves to the customer
The customer will have the order and after completion he/she requests a bill
The manager generates the bill and issues it to the customer.
Then customer pays the bill 
